		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>First official screenshots released.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.vanguardsoh.com/screenshots.php" target="_blank">http://www.vanguardsoh.com/screenshots.php</a><br />
 <br />
To quote the screenshot page:<br />
 ____________________________________________________________  _____<br />
 <br />
Screenshots are a challenge. What to show? What not to show? When to start showing them? We ended up deciding to post a sampling of different places in Thestra. Look for more screenshots in the future, though not too often at first, and not only on the official site, but on fan sites, large gaming sites, and in game magazines as well.<br />
Also please keep in mind that, relatively speaking, Vanguard is still fairly early on – we've been working on the game only about 18 months or so. That means the tech has a long way to go too, so images should only improve going forward.<br />
<br />
Lastly, we are releasing these shots in celebration of reaching our most recent major milestone, in which we delivered a 'playable alpha' of sorts. Both Microsoft and Sigil employees can log in to Vanguard, create characters, level up, trade, buy, sell, fight monsters, craft, and hone their skills (and, really more – the list goes on and on).<br />
<br />
So, in that sense, it's only fair that we share a little bit of the game with all of you – enjoy!<br />
<br />
(NOTE: Other than adding the Sigil logo, all screenshots are in-game and un-enhanced.)</div>
	</td>
